{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HGN1DKbzbMbq1RxzBmTWT4","type":"tool_result","content":"sources/rng-utopia/CLAUDE.md:62:| Emerald (tier 5) | Platinum |\nsources/rng-utopia/docs/PRODUCTION_SPEC.md:17:The platform launches with five games. All games use a shared tier system — Iron ($0.50), Bronze ($1), Silver ($5), Gold ($10), Emerald ($25), and Diamond ($100) — so players always know the exact wager amount before entering.\nsources/rng-utopia/docs/PRODUCTION_SPEC.md:57:Visual loot tiers (cosmetic, based on total damage): Bronze ($0+), Silver ($10+), Gold ($25+), Emerald ($50+), Diamond ($100+).\nsources/rng-utopia/docs/PRODUCTION_SPEC.md:92:Players earn XP at a rate of 100 XP per $1 wagered, with a +50% bonus for wins. Tier multipliers scale the earning rate further — 1x for Iron/Bronze, 1.5x for Silver, 2x for Gold, 3x for Emerald, and 5x for Diamond. Levels follow a quadratic curve (XP = 50L² + 50L) with no cap.\nsources/rng-utopia/docs/PRODUCTION_SPEC.md:94:Leveling unlocks cosmetic avatars along \"The Path of the Doge\" — 13 doge-themed avatar tiers from Recruit (Lv1) through Cosmic Deity (Lv100). Profile borders also upgrade at milestones: Iron at Lv5, Silver at Lv10, Gold at Lv15, Emerald at Lv20, Diamond at Lv25.\nsources/rng-utopia/docs/COINFLIP.md:19:| Emerald | 25 |\nsources/rng-utopia/docs/GAME_OF_TRADES.md:15:| Emerald | 25 |\nsources/rng-utopia/docs/LORD_OF_THE_RNGS.md:19:| Emerald | 25 |\nsources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx:70:• Emerald: $150-$500 damage\nsources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx:94:• Emerald: $25\nsources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/boss-raid/types.ts:52:  green_dragon: \"A venomous dragon cloaked in emerald scales, breathing toxic green flames\",\nsources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/crypto-crash/components/CrashChart.tsx:13:  up: \"#45b058\", // Emerald"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_011X2vfMQ7wLGw3N4kVTd65Y","session_id":"4fd152a2-4a58-4084-a699-69f49332660a","uuid":"e49ca190-561c-45e0-b5a3-7b41c4f596a1"}
